	<p><em><strong>X X</strong> replies:</em> Au contraire! There is - if you spoil your ballot paper, it has to be counted as such. It's far better than not voting if you disapprove of all the candidates, as you're showing that you're not apathetic, just disapproving...</p>
	<small>
	written 14th Apr 2005 <!-- | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=811&amp;commentid=758">abusive?</a>
