	<p><em><strong>ABC</strong> replies:</em> No, it shows you can spoil a paper. So either you're childish, too dim to figure out how to tick a box correctly, or a hamster seeking bedding.</p>
	<small>
	written 15th Apr 2005 <!-- | <a
